Congratulations on completing
your LinkedIn profile.

00:00:03.410 --> 00:00:06.450
As you continue your job hunt,
remember your three Rs,

00:00:06.450 --> 00:00:08.290
reflect, research, and relate.

00:00:09.570 --> 00:00:12.865
Revisit this exercise, and make sure
your professional materials line up to

00:00:12.865 --> 00:00:14.335
